data.description: Welcome home to this 3 bedroom 2.5 bath corner home lot in Spanaway. This super spacious home not only has an over sized living room-perfect for hosting. But also has a bonus living room on the second level. Secondary bedrooms  with Jack & Jill bathroom, and primary bedroom with full en-suite bath. Also features a large fully fenced yard with a patio, perfect for entertaining. Attached 2 car garage. New Roof in 2019 & New main level carpet in 2020.  Close to shopping, restaurants, JBLM, and more! Come check it out!
